{
  "stem": "7415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was terrible time, when my mother went out, and I was in the cellar alone, and-- because it was cold.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always worried that she will be killed, and I will be alone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes to-- to make myself feel warm, there was-- I knew how to boil the water, how to make water warm.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was putting the water warm in the container and put my feet in it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It was like in Andersen story about little match-- matches when she was trying to-- to make herself warmer, if you know the story.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, I was putting my feet into warm water, and that felt so good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And very often, I-- I fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was one of the worst feeling, when you wake up with your feet in cold water and no mother, and it's dark, and it's hungry.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you worry, kind of, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a lot of enjoyment when she came, [LAUGHS] you know, that she's still alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wasn't an easy kid at the time, but my mother was always there for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when it came to August '44, summer of '44, there was an uprising in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was close to the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were no ghettos and there were no Jews, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were all, you know, Polish people were fighting in Warsaw uprising in '44.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my mother-- it was a lot of bombing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a lot of prayer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The whole city was destroyed, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And at this time, nobody was really talking about the Jews so much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Or I don't remember that-- that people were blackmailing me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were just taken with other Poles.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
